{
  "texts": [
    "The number of matching tweets |Pos(q i)| was again determined by the Tweet counts endpoint; subsequently, we calculated a downsampling coefficient, as given by α = 100k |Pos(q i)|.",
    "This coefficient was then used to determine the number of tweets that should be retrieved for every single day of the story period, thereby maintaining representativity.",
    "EvaluationTo evaluate the ACR method, we considered a set of indicators, which will be explained in further detail in the following sections.",
    "Those indicators were deducible from the proposed mathematical framework and contribute to validating the ACR method.",
    "Initially, however, we present a set of descriptive statistics to objectively characterize our dataset."
  ]
